              <!-- ... previous code ... -->

              <!-- Contact Content -->
              <div class="contact-content">
                  <h2>WE’D LOVE TO HEAR FROM YOU</h2>

                  <p><i><strong>Arte</strong> would love to help answer any questions you may have.</i></p>

                  <p>Send us an email, and we’ll get back to you shortly. Also, make sure to follow us on Instagram and like our Facebook page for updates and happenings (which is a rare sight since we are just too busy making stuff)!</p>
